{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE2Mg_0019","text":"然而停下半秒 偏聽到我在哭 念着愛的廣告","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["現實","悲傷","回憶","愛的廣告"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["然而","停下","哭","念","愛","廣告"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,0,2,4,5,3,3,4,5,2,3,2,2,4,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin4","ji4","ting4","haa6","bun3","miu5","pin1","ting1","dou3","ngo5","zoi6","huk1","nim6","zoek6","oi3","dik1","gwong2","gou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"然而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"停下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"半秒","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"偏","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"聽到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"在","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"哭","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"念","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"廣告","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"再次以「然而」轉折，強調內心的真實悲傷，並將對愛的思念比喻為「廣告」，語氣更加深沉和痛苦。"},"source":{"title":"新廣告歌","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["流行","情歌","悲傷"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2162","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE2Mg_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE2Mg_0020","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE2Mg_0020","text":"如像買與賣 退貨吧若不滿足","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["關係","買賣","不滿足","退貨"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["買賣","退貨","不滿足"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,5,2,4,4,2,2,3,5,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","zoeng6","maai5","jyu5","maai6","teoi3","fo3","baa6","joek6","bat1","mun5","zuk1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"買","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"與","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"賣","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"退貨","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"吧","pos":"PART"},{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"滿足","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"將愛情關係比喻為買賣，提出「退貨」的概念，表達對關係的不滿和結束的意願，語氣決絕而悲傷。"},"source":{"title":"新廣告歌","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["流行","情歌","悲傷"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2162","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE2Mg_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE2Mg_0021","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
